title: Rick Ross - Deeper Than Rap *2009*
description:
Deeper Than Rap is the third studio album by Miami rapper Rick Ross. It is also the name of a tell-all book written by the mother of Ross's child. The album was set to be released on March 24, 2009, but has been pushed back and is now scheduled to be released on April 21, 2009. This album is set to be released under his own label, Maybach Music Group, unlike his previous releases with Slip-N-Slide Records.
